Second Department,

February, 1957

(February 11, 1957)* The People of the State of New York ex rel. Celia Goldeng, Also Known as Clara Celia Golden, Appellant, against John F. McNeill, as Director of Matteawan State Hospital, Respondent.

Motion for change of venue denied. Present — Nolan, P. J., Wenzel, Beldock, Hallinan and Kleinfeld, JJ.
